@{ViewData["Title"] = "Models - Filter";}
<h3>@ViewData["Title"]</h3>
<p>
    A Filter sets the context for an event or a subscription - that is when a subscription is created it will have a Filter that
    for example defines a location; that same Filter will be set for events that are emitted.
</p>
<p>
    This Filter is set as the <b>filter</b> property on an <a href="/models/Event">Event</a> or a <a href="/models/Subscription">Subscription</a>.
</p>
<p>
    This requires one of the following event types to be set as the <b>data</b> property:
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/models/Waste/Event">Waste Event</a></li>
    </ul>
</p>
